 &lt;svg class="octicon octicon-link" viewBox="0 0 16 16" version="1.1" width="16" height="16" aria-hidden="true"&gt;&lt;path d="m7.775 3.275 1.25-1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1 4.95 4.95l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1-4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1 .018-1.042.751.751 0 0 1 1.042-.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l2.5-2.5a2.002 2.002 0 0 0-2.83-2.83l-1.25 1.25a.751.751 0 0 1-1.042-.018.751.751 0 0 1-.018-1.042Zm-4.69 9.64a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 2.83 0l1.25-1.25a.751.751 0 0 1 1.042.018.751.751 0 0 1 .018 1.042l-1.25 1.25a3.5 3.5 0 1 1-4.95-4.95l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 4.95 0 .751.751 0 0 1-.018 1.042.751.751 0 0 1-1.042.018 1.998 1.998 0 0 0-2.83 0l-2.5 2.5a1.998 1.998 0 0 0 0 2.83Z"&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;曾经对佛学感兴趣，对寺庙一直感觉亲近。十一之前，就想着找个寺庙玩玩，跟hh说了这个想法后，hh说：&amp;ldquo;十一去径山寺吧&amp;rdquo;，就埋下了径山寺之行的种子。本打算十一假期最后两天去的，可惜，hh身体不太舒服，没有成行；再后来，天气转凉，hh感冒了，久未痊愈，就把径山寺这事放下了。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>游法镜寺记</title><link>https://simplecoding.fun/posts/2017/08/visit-fajing-temple/</link><pubDate>Sun, 13 Aug 2017 09:49:53 +0800</pubDate><author>fighter9010@gmail.com (lazypanda)</author><guid>https://simplecoding.fun/posts/2017/08/visit-fajing-temple/</guid><category domain="https://simplecoding.fun/categories/%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/">生活</category><description>&lt;p&gt;法镜寺，位于西湖之西，群山之下。清乾隆时得名，曾遭战火，光绪时重建。又名下天竺寺，为杭州唯一之女众寺院。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>随笔-2017-08-03</title><link>https://simplecoding.fun/posts/2017/08/journal-2017-08-03/</link><pubDate>Thu, 03 Aug 2017 10:00:26 +0800</pubDate><author>fighter9010@gmail.com (lazypanda)</author><guid>https://simplecoding.fun/posts/2017/08/journal-2017-08-03/</guid><category domain="https://simplecoding.fun/categories/%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/">生活</category><description>&lt;p&gt;近日，心颇不安定。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>随笔-2017-08-02</title><link>https://simplecoding.fun/posts/2017/08/journal-2017-08-02/</link><pubDate>Wed, 02 Aug 2017 10:06:51 +0800</pubDate><author>fighter9010@gmail.com (lazypanda)</author><guid>https://simplecoding.fun/posts/2017/08/journal-2017-08-02/</guid><category domain="https://simplecoding.fun/categories/%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/">生活</category><description>&lt;p&gt;少年时，便觉得诗词是最美的文字。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>元宵夜感</title><link>https://simplecoding.fun/posts/2010/02/lantern-festival-thoughts/</link><pubDate>Sun, 28 Feb 2010 20:08:00 +0800</pubDate><author>fighter9010@gmail.com (lazypanda)</author><guid>https://simplecoding.fun/posts/2010/02/lantern-festival-thoughts/</guid><category domain="https://simplecoding.fun/categories/%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/">生活</category><description>&lt;p&gt;很久没有这么正儿八经的写日志了 要想找不写的理由 总是能找出一大堆来 但归根结底还是因为自己懒 其实有时候挺想用文字记下生活的点滴 怕岁月会淡忘掉一切 但最终还是没有写&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>